{"tid":681214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多口叫情侶分手 P牌寶馬男揭酒駕被捕","createTime":"2018-05-28T00:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T01:22:05.000Z","uid":122,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a14f6c24851646fb7a6b63a3372c9fbfcb3ab165","tid":681214,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:21:58.000Z","msg":"荃灣馬頭壩道，昨晚約11時半，一名姓黃(41歲)P牌寶馬司機，發現一對情侶在路邊爭執，於是落車介入勸解。其間黃叫二人分手，結果觸怒姓林(25歲)男事主，雙方起爭執大打出手，同樣臉及腳受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，調查下發現黃未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌酒後駕駛，另外亦與林涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕，案件由荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14765f799d93c89db2ccc07b624bcb72564af92a","tid":681214,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"真係飲撚大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfcdaa5b1890e67b5932e4440579914c44b4903","tid":681214,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"傻鳩.."},{"pid":"2f6061aaa99514f91c7342c600e7adab2f6d8b0a","tid":681214,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8feca96d262159a1ce95895d017303d35ca9f3","tid":681214,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7abb822b634b4551a643309d874afc26c74c18b","tid":681214,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"條友飲大左 幾玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780acbb3b31871c644692277e0026459a2161e8d","tid":681214,"uid":86756,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:37:44.000Z","msg":"41歲被捕（P牌)"},{"pid":"60c52f3a3e0e9fcb1fc